Radio Show Team






Host
James G. Meredith, CPA/PFS
Jim, the creator of "Your Money and You," has over 30 years broadcast experience and has been one of the firm's leaders since 1977. Jim has been ranked for multiple years on Barron's Top 100 Independent Wealth Advisors in America.









Co-Host
Raymond Ballantine, CFP®
As one of our newer co-hosts, Ray brings over 30 years investment advisory experience, beginning his career in 1986 with a major Wall Street brokerage house.







Co-Host
Kurt Carlson, CFP®, CFA®, AIFA®
Kurt has been an active member of the firm since 1990, gaining numerous professional designations to accompany his time spent in Pakistan where his parents worked as missionaries.







Co-Host
Jayme Meredith, CFA®
With over 100 annual media appearances, Jayme is one of the region’s "go-to" financial experts, including regular speaking engagements and news outlet interviews.







Co-Host
Belynda Slaugenhaupt, CFP®
A popular voice of KDKA's daily afternoon stock report, Belynda has a dynamic background with experience serving local governments and a commitment to philanthropy.







Co-Host
Tyler Vallano, CFP®
Tyler started his Hefren-Tillotson career as an intern, working to earn his Certified Financial Planner designation and become a full-time advisor dedicated to providing a superior client experience.







Producer
Mary Ann Siebert, CFP®
As the show's producer, Mary Ann oversees the making of "Your Money & You" in addition to regularly broadcasts of daily stock reports and"Ask the Advisor" segments.












